{"tid":1375302,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[第2x個post]JYPE 對 MINA 健康情況及成員惡評者正式提出告訴","createTime":"2019-07-28T04:29:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T05:07:26.000Z","uid":238483,"like":8,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c8bbe3fb9279853c56a5747837cfd041ae9cecb2","tid":1375302,"uid":238483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:29:07.000Z","msg":"JYP Entertainment 曾宣布將對關於 TWICE Mina 健康有關的惡評採取法律行動，昨日 (26日)，公司發表了聲明向粉絲們更新情況。聲明如下：<br />\n「大家好，這裡是 JYPE。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zRc8Yku.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzRc8Yku.gif&h=df00e7da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在宣布我們將對7月11日公開的 Mina 健康情況，以及相關話題中牽涉到其他成員的惡意貼文與評論採取法律行動後，我們透過自己的監控與粉絲提供的情報確認了相關證據，現已提起刑事告訴。<br />\n我們要再次聲明，為了保護旗下藝人的名譽與權利，我們會繼續採取可能的民事與刑事訴訟。<span style=\"color: red;\">我們請求粉絲們主動提供情報</span>。<br />\n謝謝各位。」<br />\n7月11日，JYP Entertainment 宣布&nbsp;Mina 因突如其來的舞台恐慌症將暫停活動，並將缺席接下來的 TWICE 世界巡迴演唱會《TWICE World Tour 2019 &quot;TWICELIGHTS&quot;》。<br />\nKpopn 的 D.W. 報導<br />\n❁ 轉載請註明&nbsp;Kpopn&nbsp;與所有來源 ❁<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.kpopn.com/amp/2019/07/27/jyp-entertainment-sues-twice-mina-malicious-comments\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kpopn.com%2Famp%2F2019%2F07%2F27%2Fjyp-entertainment-sues-twice-mina-malicious-comments&d=GsYKB4iL2zhb3369BxXbpzcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=5678a2ef\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.kpopn.com/amp/2019/07/27/jyp-entertainment-sues-twice-mina-malicious-comments</a><br />\n各位反導嘅會員識做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"748b44d74c6f1df95208e2a759bd763e6eb972a0","tid":1375302,"uid":143093,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:31:23.000Z","msg":"不分化 不割蓆 不篤灰🙏🏻<br />\n香港加油🇭🇰💪🏻"},{"pid":"0df996bc4a8e0a6de80e297188f06339152ea39a","tid":1375302,"uid":76632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"748b44d74c6f1df95208e2a759bd763e6eb972a0","tid":1375302,"uid":143093,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"cit